## Limitations

This report is based on available data up to October 2023 and may not reflect the most current developments in supply chain dynamics. Additionally, the information is drawn from secondary sources, which may have inherent biases or limitations in scope. Further research and real-time data analysis would be necessary for a more comprehensive understanding of the ongoing shortages.